46
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:37,421
Bill and Joyce have been wonderful friends to Tufts and to the greater community.

47
00:04:38,041 --> 00:04:41,902
Their philanthropy has been transformational to our university,

48
00:04:42,804 --> 00:04:45,965
