63
00:06:30,201 --> 00:06:34,744
We appreciate their willingness to work with us as we continue to refine our plan.

64
00:06:35,805 --> 00:06:44,172
Neither the Tufts Building nor its amenities would be possible without the significant work of the MBTA that they've already done on the College Ave Station.

65
00:06:45,012 --> 00:06:54,079
The MBTA has been a true partner as this project has developed and we look forward to completion of our building when the T Station opens at the end of 2020.

66
00:06:54,119 --> 00:06:57,782
It is a very exciting project.

67
00:06:58,217 --> 00:07:05,379
And I look forward to the day we can all assemble again to dedicate the vision of Bill Cummings, which is finally brought to fruition.

68
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:06,619
