96
00:10:08,398 --> 00:10:09,179
We thank you for that.

97
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:17,727
The agreement between Tufts and the MBTA commits Tufts to cover all additional project costs implemented on the University's behalf.

98
00:10:18,307 --> 00:10:31,559
